description: ~ The Tastiest Cupcakes In The South Bay ~ As a little girl born in Hollywood and raised in the South Bay, Seansay has always liked to put smiles on peoples faces by making them her tasty treats. Now with all of that loving experience behind her, she has found a way to put permanent smiles on everyone's faces. People would be surprised to find out how much of her heart Seansay puts into each one of these delectable desserts.Amazingly many have even said that her cupcakes are actually blessed.So come share in the experience and tell your friends and family about us.Thank you for visiting and Have a Wonderful and Blessed day!
name: Royal Red Velvet
